Returns the iterator pointing past the last entry of the {{tt|basic_stacktrace}}. 

This iterator acts as a placeholder; attempting to dereference it results in undefined behavior. 

{{image|range-begin-end.svg}}

===Parameters===
(none)

===Return value===
The end iterator.

===Complexity===
Constant.
